        <abstract>
            <p>Thanks for specimens of cirripedes attached to rocks, which show no boring. CD hopes to see some on limestone.</p> 
<p>Encourages CSB to do research on the complemental males of <hi rend="italic">Scalpellum vulgare</hi>.</p> 
